Author: Jim Fitzpatrick
Message:
Replace testling with tape-run

Replace testling, used by `npm test`, with tape-run, an alternative tape
test runner that defaults to Electron. testling frequently seems to
leave zombie processes around, and is currently abandoned.

See https://github.com/substack/testling/issues/111
